        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-7">
          <p>
            Our mission at EverWash is to create happy and delightful experiences for all of our stakeholders. Creating delightful experiences for all our customers at every touch point means providing the right kind of support to car wash operators at every stage of their business lifecycle. For our customers and members, this means delivering human-centered experiences that delight. For our employees, this means fostering a culture of collaboration, open communication, excellence, and balance.
          </p>
          <p>
            EverWash partners with local car washes to offer unlimited car washes for a low monthly fee. Using an app, we help our customers save and enjoy their cars. Over time, our capabilities have expanded to include an end-to-end solution for managing customer interactions and delivering data-based recommendations for improving car wash performance. Our commitment to helping wash operators increase revenue-generating potential through smart analytics and customer-centric marketing continues to be relentless. Car washing should be enjoyable and carefree.
          </p>
